snippet.title: Monster Train - Launch Trailer | PS5 Games
snippet.description:
At long last, Monster Train has arrived on PlayStation 5! Hell has frozen over. Only you can protect the final burning pyre from the forces of heaven and restore the inferno. Monster Train brings a new strategic layer to roguelike deck building, with three vertical play fields to defend.

#ps5 #ps5games #monstertrain
